claim.claim-text:
1. A method for determining a phase shift of an optical signal, said method comprising the steps of:
inducing, a temporal phase shift into the optical signal;
converting, the phase modulation of the optical signal into an intensity modulation;
measuring, the intensity modulated signal; and
determining, the phase shift of the optical signal from the intensity measurement(s).

where
I is the intensity of the optical signal;
ψ is the phase of the optical signal;
φ(2) is the second order dispersion of the medium; and
is the time.
